    "The impact of embeddings on our judges is investigated in Figures 8 and 9.",
    "Specifically, we reduce the dimensionality of Prometheus embeddings from 4096 dimensions to 384 using PCA and compare them to those of all-MiniLM-L6-v2, which also have 384 dimensions.",
